text: Welcome home! Spectacular & well cared for 4 bed/2.25 bath, 2 story home w/ finished basement & 3 car garage in the coveted Thunderbird community. Private 1/3-acre lot + minutes from I-5 & downtown MV. Front door opens to massive family room w/ wood burning stove, vaulted ceilings & custom tile. Kitchen features stainless steel appliances & granite countertops. Main level opens to a spacious 800 sq ft deck w/ Mt Baker views. Upstairs features: primary bedroom w/ walk in closet + an additional bedroom. Downstairs features fully finished additional living space: 3/4 bath, bedroom, sizable living area & a game room. Great natural lighting and storage all throughout home. All bedrooms feature a patio or private balcony. A must see!

Welcome to your personal paradise, nestled on nearly 2 acres of stunning land. This charming home boasts breathtaking views of farmlands, mountains, and the surrounding area. Step into a backyard designed for hosting lively gatherings, complete with a gazebo and patio ideal for making lasting memories. Inside, revel in the luxurious and cozy finishes that create a sense of opulence. The stylish and elegant interior will captivate all who enter. Additionally, the well-maintained original barn on the premises offers ample storage space.

Location and access to the freeway are everything! Join this little townhome community tucked away into a great neighborhood. This one is a real value. SFR not a condo with low HOA dues that covers lawn care, exterior maintenance on home & common areas. Exterior is getting painted this summer by HOA. Priced well for some built in equity. Situated as an end unit at the end of a dead-end street with a private park. Features 1566 sq ft, 3 Bedrooms, 2.5 Baths, 1 car garage. Kitchen is open to dining & living room custom cabinets, granite counters & a pantry. Spacious primary bedroom with walk in closet. Eligible for Zero Down 100% USDA financing!

Rare opportunity to buy highly sought-after North Shore Lake Cavanaugh cabin. Great beach with oversized dock, boat lift and Sea-do lift. Adorable cabin features living area with fireplace, dining area, well-equipped kitchen, main bedroom w/french doors that open to hot tub on the covered iron wood deck. Additional bedroom with built-in bunk beds, laundry room also used as bedroom. Heated 1600 sq ft. garage that includes 324 sq. ft. media room with propane fireplace, built in wine/beverage cooler and 1/2 bath. 30 amp RV hookup with sewer drain. All of this on 2 level lots, This one will go fast so don't dawdle!

Rambler, with fully fenced large level lot and plenty of garden space. Two driveways (1) is covered and fenced for your RV/boat parking and (1) for the double car garage with shop space. Formal living room with gas fireplace and large windows for bird watching. Kitchen w/garden window opens to the great room with sliding glass doors to a huge covered deck with skylights. Bonus room thru french doors in great room can be used as an office with an exterior door. Primary bdrm with en-suite bath, primary walk in closet was converted to shelving for storage and 2 closets were added in the bedroom. Home was once 3 bdrms and can be again by adding a wall in the formal dining room. Public transit at the corner Route#300. Stores and eateries near by.

An absolute legacy property perched on the Anacortes coastline & overlooking the Guemes Channel & San Juans. Breathtaking Northwest & sunset views. 8, 712 SF Main Residence features 5 BR's, each w/an ensuite bathroom. Chefs kitchen for the absolute finest culinary experience. Private theater, game room, elevator, 3rd floor rec room + a 180 degree lookout tower. The estate includes a luxurious guest house (1300+ /sf), enormous 4-car garage, + separate 1064 SF Manager's house. NO expense spared. ALL impeccable & shows as if brand new. 2+ AC of arboretum-like grounds. 230' of deeded tidelands. Board your private yacht or the Anacortes ferry....marinas/terminal are minutes away. Truly one of the most iconic waterfront estates in the PNW.

Situated in a desirable cul-de-sac in Burlington, this charming home rests on a spacious 1/3-acre lot at the end of a quiet dead-end street. The 3-bed, 2-bath, 1218 SF floor plan invites you in with a cozy living room that flows seamlessly into the kitchen, dining room, and second living/family room. Recent updates include fresh carpeting, both interior and exterior paint, and an updated septic. The primary bedroom features an en suite bathroom for added convenience. Venture outside to a large patio and a HUGE fully fenced backyard, perfect for outdoor activities and gatherings. Come see it for yourself!

Retreat into delightful living amidst nature's grandeur nestled on 5 acres at the end of a secluded road. Every detail exudes warmth & quiet elegance, from wood accents to vaulted ceilings. Open floor plan was designed for entertaining w/ Mount Baker views from almost every room. Gourmet kitchen includes striking rustic alder cabinetry, an expansive island, and high-end appliances. The primary suite beckons repose w/ custom walk-in closet and a cozy fireplace. Relax on the flagstone patio or unwind by the fire pit surrounded by a landscaped oasis with automated irrigation. An exceptionally crafted ADU and an oversized shop with a half basketball court complete the property. Welcome to your haven of refined comfort and endless possibilities.

Camp-A-lot in the Cascade River Park! This well-built 2 bed 2 bath custom rambler is turnkey, and this is the first time it has been available on the market. You can use it for year around living, a vacation home, or short-term rental. This home features a spacious and quiet lot, with plenty of parking for all your guests. RV hook up, new hot water tank, recently serviced and inspected septic system, metal roof, cedar siding, solar ready, solar panels installed. Features vaulted ceilings and a fresh coat of paint. Excellent location close to hiking, fishing, boating, and is a great mountain retreat to create memories for years to come. A must see in Marblemount!

Your new Pied--terre! A totally remodeled 1930s bungalow just steps from the beaches of Anacortes Washington Park. A private water view deck out front w/ French doors. Inside, cathedral ceilings & plank flooring in great room w/tiled fireplace surround, kitchen w/eating space & new lighting, a new fridge & dishwasher. A unique tapestry room divider, bath w/new tiled-in shower, laundry & walk-in closet space. Outside, surrounded by a private fenced-in patio, new landscaping & lighting in the terraced gardens & greenhouse, a fun sidewalk fire-pit next to a custom concrete driveway. Simply remarkable & charming beyond belief. You can walk to the Washington State ferry for a trip to the San Juans. Next door MLS 2244567 4 sale.

Welcome to this tastefully remodeled home in the heart of Sedro-Woolley! Renovated in 2020, this home has many modern upgrades while preserving some of its charming original features. Enjoy a stunning kitchen with ample cabinets with under lighting, granite countertops & stainless steel appliances. The home features elegant tile & low-maintenance laminate flooring throughout. Extra finished room with exterior entrance offers the potential for a small home based business. The spacious fully fenced backyard has nice privacy, perfect for relaxation or entertaining. There is room to grow, build a garden or shop. Great location, with close proximity to town & all amenities. Dont miss out on this perfect blend of modern comfort & classic charm!

Location, location, location! A diamond in the rough on the hill, near hospital & other medical facilities. Minutes from I-5! This studio home features a Murphy bed, full bath, & a roomy kitchen. Newer roof in 2020, natural gas free-standing heater (worked on in 2020). Backyard offers raised beds, small dog house, portable carport (stays) & several outbuildings - one was used as a nice shop. Alley access in back of house. Thinking of going tiny? This place has the potential to be a darling home, it just needs your creativity!

This is an amazing opportunity to own in the coveted neighborhood of Clearidge in Anacortes. A 3 Bedroom and 2.5 Bathrooms with 1, 870 SQFT. move in ready home. Access to pickle-ball and tennis courts as well as basketball courts just around the corner. Come see why Clearidge is a sought after area to live!

Explore the possibilities of this expansive/private 37.25 acres consisting of 2 parcels. Quiet location on a low traffic road minutes to I-5 just South of Bellingham. Parcel #1 is 17.25 acres with relics of an older home, barn and outbuildings. Property had use of well, septic and power but not for many years. One acre of Parcel #1 is taxed at market rate, the rest enjoys low taxation as it is designated open space/ag. Parcel #2 is also open space/ag designation and is 20 acres and sits just above Parcel #1. Possible seller financing options. Sold as is estate sale. Buyer to sign continuance of OSAG designation prior to closing.

An Anacortes icon on Sunset Avenue, just a stones throw from the beaches of Washington Park. Main-level living throughout, a beautifully refreshed 1940s-era 2bed, 1bath home, fronted by its unique arbor, a south-facing glassed-in deck with peek-a-boo view. Cozy great room w/fireplace & triple-pane windows, dining area, new kitchen w/sit-down bar, deep sink, newly-tiled backsplash, coffee/wine bar & glowing Tiffany lighting. Check out the retro-charmed detached 202sqft apartment with living, kitchen, bath, sleeping loft, skylights. Serene deck w/hot tub & hanging vines right out the back door. Low-maintenance stone landscaping, plus 2 fenced-in decks. Garage/workshop. Stroll to & from San Juan ferry. Next door MLS#2244566 also 4 sale.

Charming, bright Mount Vernon mid-century rambler with beautiful original hardwood floors throughout, fresh interior paint, & stone surround wood burning fireplace! Kitchen features a moveable island for additional counter space & storage as well as a freestanding dishwasher. Large storage closets can be found throughout the home as well as in the full bathroom which also features a double sink, shower, & tub. Spend time sitting on your front deck or go out the back sliding glass door off the dining area to the welcoming fully fenced backyard with mature landscaping and both deck & patio for lounging and entertaining! Attached one car garage with storage, work space, and shop sink. Additional parking available alongside the garage as well!

True gem! Beautiful and well-appointed Christenson Home built with elegant features such as crown molding, Brazilian cherry wood floors and coffered ceilings. The gourmet kitchen features Viking appliances, granite counters , wet bar & walk-in pantry-delightful for any chef. Amazing views of the islands and San Juan ferry, especially from living room and 2nd great room. The layout, with formal and informal spaces, is ideal for both entertaining and everyday living. Second-level covered veranda to enjoy morning coffee or afternoon tea. The primary bedroom on the main level leads out to patio. Oversized garage provides ample space for hobbies. Steps away from Anacortes Community Forest Lands & local trail head to Cranberry Lake.

Ideally located 3 bd 2 Bath beautiful spacious newer home with an open floor plan. Walk to parks, restaurants, library, soccer fields front row seats to local events. Home features solar panels lowering utility bill to $8 per month average. Open kitchen large granite island, granite counter tops throughout, Freshly painted decks, 220V in garage/shop. RV parking, 900sq unfinished basement waiting for your touch. Newly finished 230sq ft office/den/under stairs nook. Fruit trees, garden space and additional parking. This home is beautiful and move in ready!

Large and lovely Park Village home with lots of updates! Updated kitchen with new countertops and large 2 door pantry. Large living, dining rooms and family room area that opens up to new deck to enjoy the sunshine. Both bedrooms have updated bathrooms and large walk in shower off primary. Even more updates with new roof and windows, new paint throughout, new lighting, doors and deck sliders, plus new decks and low maintenance landscaping. Tankless gas water heater and heatpump for comfortable living. Nice storage/shop plus garden shed. This homes neat and tidy landscaped back area opens up to a large and grassy green belt great for walking Rover or Sparky! Truly a must see!

Charming Country Home...2 bedrooms, 1 bath, spacious kitchen with gas range, dishwasher, refrigerator, lots of counter space. Living room with beautiful westerly views & sunsets. New septic & drain field in 2020, new Visqueen and insulation in crawlspace. Fully fenced yard with detached 2 door garage, works great for 1 car and shop space. Could be modified for 2 cars. Convenient to I-5 and minutes to town.

Welcome to this charming and well-appointed home in the perfect location! This remodeled Gem in Old Town boasts classic details at every turn and has been given an artistic touch. The stylish kitchen will make doing dishes a pleasure, while the main level features 2 bedrooms, a full bath, hardwood floors, a quaint office, and a cozy living room with gas fireplace. Outside, the mature landscaping creates a serene oasis, perfect for entertaining. A recently added exterior back deck offers peek-a-boo views of the Guemes Channel. The fully fenced, manicured yard and the downstairs bonus shop are a rare find. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this home yours.

Perfectly situated rambler in quiet Brickyard Creek cul-de-sac. Extra generous living room with picturesque bay windows. Living and dining space leads into large kitchen overlooking a family room. Three bedrooms, two baths including a private primary suite at the end of the hall. House comes complete with 2 year new roof, efficient hydronic heating, RV parking, and 94 x 155 outbuilding. Fresh interior paint and stainless steel appliances. Heating system recently fully inspected and serviced. Private backyard with mature landscaping and partially fenced. Close to Sedro amenities, hospital, and downtown shopping.

A rare opportunity awaits to own your own compound nestled on 20 acres overlooking the Skagit River, with breathtaking views of Sauk Mountain and Mount Baker. The property boasts a variety of fruit trees including apple, cherry, plum, pear, and peach, as well as enchanting Korean spice trees emitting a delightful aroma. The cabin is connected to electricity, and a 700-gallon water catchment system ensures a renewable water source. Featuring three cabins, a cook shack, and a 14x60 storage container for added convenience. Secluded yet conveniently located just 1.5 miles from town, with easy access to schools, shopping, medical facilities, and recreational areas. Situated only 1.25 miles from Lake Shannon. Schedule your private tour today!

Welcome to your new home, a sanctuary designed to reflect your elevated lifestyle. Nestled in the Summer Ridge neighborhood, this timeless residence reflects both elegance and modern sophistication. An airy and inviting atmosphere will welcome you home, where the soft ambiance invites relaxation & intimate gatherings. The kitchen is equipped to meet every culinary need with style and ease and is where cherished memories are made. Indulge in the newly remodeled bathrooms which boast both modern design and ultimate relaxation. W/ every detail impeccably curated, you'll realize this is the home you've been waiting for. A large .67 acre lot, fully fenced-in backyard, RV parking, wood floors & central A/C make this home, absolute perfection.

Welcome to this charming Anacortes home, ideally located just a block away from Volunteer-Kiwanis Meadow Park and a few minutes to downtown. This one-level living gem features a delightful front deck, a covered back patio, and a cozy sunroom. The backyard is a gardener's paradise, boasting beautiful flowers, fruit trees, and a greenhouse. This home also includes a huge bedroom or bonus room with a private entrance, perfect for flex space or a caretaker's bedroom. The driveway is big enough to park a small RV or boat. Conveniently located with easy access to Highway 20, this home offers the perfect blend of comfort and accessibility.

Experience the perfect blend of rural charm and urban convenience in this lovely 3-bedroom home nestled on the outskirts of town. Enjoy a quaint and welcoming neighborhood atmosphere with a hint of country vibes, while being just outside of city limits. Beyond your backyard, discover the ease of access to I5, with Burlington/Mt Vernon nearby for all your shopping needs. This single-level home is situated on a generous lot surrounded by mature vegetation, providing an escape into county living. Ideal for those craving tranquility without compromising on modern conveniences.

Nestled on 5.32 Acres, this Rare Waterfront Estate Soaks in Southerly Puget Sound & Territorial Views. 557 of Waterfront Includes Sandy Beach, Bulkhead, Boat Ramp & Two Mooring Buoys. Main Home Features Luxurious Kitchen Offering Quartzite Counters, Large Walk-in Pantry & Opens to Dining Area w/ Wet Bar. Living Room w/ Granite FP & Expansive Windows Allow Remarkable Views Throughout. Private Office w/ Built-ins, Granite FP & Patio Access. Upper Level Offers Two Guest Beds, Guest Bath & Opulent Primary Suite w/ Lrg Walk-in Shower, Soaking Tub, Heated Floors & WIC. Finished Bsmt Includes Rec Room, Bath, Laundry & Workshop. Level-Entry MIL w/ Full Bath & Water Views Above 2-Car Garage. No Ferry Required! Boat House Available, Not Included

Welcome home to the desirable neighborhood of Skagit Highlands! Enjoy all of the parks and nature trails that surround you. The backyard is a gardeners' oasis. Open floor plan concept for entertaining - The kitchen is a gourmet cooks delight - Including gas stove, large walk in pantry, plenty of counter space and all new appliances. Relax in your fully fenced, private back yard with nature surrounding you. Heat pump will keep you warm in the winter and cool in the summer. First time on market since being built. Lot next door is owned and maintained by HOA -

Nestled on a secluded acre in Conway, this charming home is surrounded by protected lots, ensuring stunning views. The single-level layout features an open design with vaulted ceilings. The custom kitchen has Thermador appliances, including double ovens, quartz countertops, and a large pantry. The primary bedroom has a walk-in closet and a master bathroom with a luxurious shower and heated tiles. It includes a cozy family room with NanaWall glass folding door bringing the outdoors in. Created for entertainment, the patio showcases an outdoor fire pit. A sizable three-car garage offers ample storage space. This property is an outstanding opportunity to own a home where comfort and convenience converge.

Minutes from I-5 this secret jewel perched a top a hillside gives you a Cabin/Chateau feel. Beautiful 3 bedroom, 1.75 bath on 1.1 acre with open floor plan, new windows throughout has a central brick fireplace, hardwood floors, beautiful cedar beams which gives you a cozy cabin feel. Open kitchen with eating space, white cabinets with pullout shelves, black appliances with the Pantry/laundry room off kitchen. The private primary bedroom with bath and sliding glass door leading to outside patio where you can enjoy your garden oasis, view the wildlife and all your beautiful flowers. Plenty of room to garden on all levels with lots of fruit trees and fruit bearing bushes. Don?t miss the Garden sheds for all you tools. Plenty of parking space.

Harvest the gold! Reimagine an era gone by w/a dash of modern touches. Featuring 1, 344 sq. ft., 3 bds, 2 full baths, new carpet throughout, this home entertains a spacious living room, formal dining /office area. A kitchen that radiates sunshine inside & out, equipped w/ an original wall oven, separate range/oven, ample cupboards for storage. Adjacent informal dining area/bonus space with slider to the deck, makes a perfect spot for hosting seasonal get-togethers. Two bedrooms, utility room, primary bedroom with an ensuite full bath. A delightful yard to enjoy the glow of the Summer sun, 2 sheds to store extra belongings. Pre-inspected, no HOA, fee simple lot, close to all amenities/services, on a dead end street. Welcome home!

NEW PRICE PLUS BUYER INCENTIVES!!! Spacious Vintage home with lots of character nestled away in west Mount Vernon. Minutes away from downtown and I-5. Large kitchen with lots of cabinet space and stainless appliances. Open main living area w/ fir hardwood floors. Arches, tall ceilings & large windows allows natural light to fill this home. Big bonus room upstairs to design as you like & a large partially finished basement! Enjoy the large fenced yard with unlimited potential! Out buildings & plenty of room to park your RV.

Looking for a property where you can live comfortably, enjoy gardening, hobbies, ponds, greenhouses, nature, and more? Look no further because this is the place! This cottage property is secluded and oozes with charm and character. The home and property have been shaped and created by a true artist for several decades. Many of the structures are truly works of art! The home is much larger than the record states-nearly double in size. There's plenty of space to relax indoors with the added luxury of outbuildings big enough to enjoy your favorite hobbies, or use as guest quarters. The nearly 2.5 acres are level, wooded and offer total privacy. A winding, gated drive leads to the home off Hwy 530, just minutes from the Sauk!
